audioFeedback:
Title:
Troubleshooting SAP Commerce Cloud Marketplace Application

Summary:
The speaker describes an issue with the SAP Commerce Cloud Marketplace application, specifically a malfunction where no products appear on the selector page despite attempts to add products and refresh the page.

Description:
The audio involves a user detailing a problem encountered while using the SAP Commerce Cloud Marketplace application. The user attempts to add products, but upon clicking the 'add products' button, the selector page that opens is empty, displaying no products. Despite refreshing the page several times, the issue persists as the page continuously shows a loading sign but fails to display any products. The user expresses uncertainty about the cause of the problem.
